UserObject.plantUmlData:
{
  "data": "@startuml

actor User as U
participant TourRequestAcceptancePage as TRAP
participant TourRequestAcceptanceViewModel as TRAVM
participant SelectDateForTourRequestWindow as SDFTRW
participant SelectDateForTourRequestViewModel as SDFTRVM
participant AddTourWindow as ATW
participant AddTourViewModel as ATVM
participant LocationService as LS
participant LocationRepository as LR
participant SimpleRequestService as SRS
participant SimpleRequestRepository as SRR
collections SimpleAndComplexTourRequestsDTO as SACTR
participant TourRepository as TR
participant TourService as TS
participant CheckPointRepository as CPR
participant TourImageRepository as TIR
participant SimpleRequestTourService as SRTS
participant SimpleRequestTourRepository as SRTR

U-> TRAP ++: SearchCommand
TRAP->TRAVM ++: Search
TRAVM -> TRAVM ++: LoadRequests

TRAVM->SRS++: CreateListOfSimpleRequestsDTO()
SRS->SRR ++: GetAll()
SRR--> SRS--:simpleRequestsList
loop SimpleRequest simpleRequest in simpleRequestsList
  opt simpleRequest.Status == SimpleRequestStatus.ON_HOLD
    SRS->LS++:GetAll()
    LS->LR++: GetAll()
    
    LR--> LS--:AllLocations
    LS-->SRS--:AllLocations
    SRS->SACTR**: <<create>>ListOfSimpleRequestsDTO
    loop Location location in AllLocations
      opt location.Id==simpleRequest.Location.Id
        SRS->SACTR++:Add(simpleRequest)
        SACTR->SRS--:
        deactivate SACTR
    end
  end
  end
end

SRS-->TRAVM--: ListOfSimpleRequestsDTO

TRAVM->SACTR++: <<create>>AllRequests
deactivate SACTR
  loop foreach request in ListOfSimpleRequestsDTO()
    TRAVM-> SACTR++:Add(request)
    SACTR->TRAVM--:
    deactivate SACTR
  end
deactivate TRAVM
  opt !string.IsNullOrEmpty(SelectedState)
    TRAVM->SRS++: FilterState(List<SimpleAndComplexTourRequestsDTO> AllRequests, string SelectedState)
    SRS->SACTR++:<<create>>List
    deactivate SACTR  
    loop foreach SimpleAndComplexTourRequestsDTO request in AllRequests
      opt request.Location.State == SelectedState
        SRS-> SACTR++:Add(request)
        SACTR->SRS--:
        deactivate SACTR
      end
    end
    SRS-->TRAVM--: AllRequests
  end
  deactivate SRS
 opt !string.IsNullOrEmpty(SelectedCity)
    TRAVM->SRS++: FilterState(List<SimpleAndComplexTourRequestsDTO> AllRequests, string SelectedCity)
    SRS->SACTR++:<<create>>List
    deactivate SACTR  
    loop foreach SimpleAndComplexTourRequestsDTO request in AllRequests
      opt request.Location.City == SelectedCity
        SRS-> SACTR++:Add(request)
        SACTR->SRS--:
        deactivate SACTR
      end
    end
    SRS-->TRAVM--: AllRequests
  end
  deactivate SRS
 opt !string.IsNullOrEmpty(Language)
    TRAVM->SRS++: FilterState(List<SimpleAndComplexTourRequestsDTO> AllRequests, string SelectedLanguage)
    SRS->SACTR++:<<create>>List
    deactivate SACTR  
    loop foreach SimpleAndComplexTourRequestsDTO request in AllRequests
      opt request.Language == SelectedLanguage
        SRS-> SACTR++:Add(request)
        SACTR->SRS--:
        deactivate SACTR
      end
    end
    SRS-->TRAVM--: AllRequests
  end
  deactivate SRS
 opt !string.IsNullOrEmpty(MaxGuests)
    TRAVM->SRS++: FilterState(List<SimpleAndComplexTourRequestsDTO> AllRequests, string MaxGuests)
    SRS->SACTR++:<<create>>List
    deactivate SACTR  
    loop foreach SimpleAndComplexTourRequestsDTO request in AllRequests
      opt request.NumberOfGuests == MaxGuests
        SRS-> SACTR++:Add(request)
        SACTR->SRS--:
        deactivate SACTR
      end
    end
    SRS-->TRAVM--: AllRequests
  end
  deactivate SRS
 opt SelectedStartDate.Date>=DateTime.Now
    TRAVM->SRS++: FilterState(List<SimpleAndComplexTourRequestsDTO> AllRequests, DateTime SelectedStartDate)
    SRS->SACTR++:<<create>>List
    deactivate SACTR  
    loop foreach SimpleAndComplexTourRequestsDTO request in AllRequests
      opt request.StartDate.Date == SelectedStartDate.Date
        SRS-> SACTR++:Add(request)
        SACTR->SRS--:
        deactivate SACTR
      end
    end
    SRS-->TRAVM--: AllRequests
  end
  deactivate SRS
opt SelectedEndDate.Date!= SelectedStartDate.Date
    TRAVM->SRS++: FilterState(List<SimpleAndComplexTourRequestsDTO> AllRequests,DateTime SelectedEndDate)
    SRS->SACTR++:<<create>>List
    deactivate SACTR  
    loop foreach SimpleAndComplexTourRequestsDTO request in AllRequests
      opt request.SelectedEndDate.Date == SelectedEndDate.Date
        SRS-> SACTR++:Add(request)
        SACTR->SRS--:
        deactivate SACTR
      end
    end
    SRS-->TRAVM--: AllRequests
  end
  deactivate SRS
TRAVM-->TRAP--: AllRequests
deactivate TRAVM
TRAP-->U--: Display AllRequests
deactivate TRAP

U->TRAP ++:AcceptCommand
activate TRAP
TRAP->TRAVM ++: AcceptSimpleTourRequest
activate TRAVM
TRAVM->SDFTRW ++: SelectTourRequest
SDFTRW->SDFTRVM++:CreateTour
SDFTRVM->TS ++: CheckAvailability(SelectedDate)
TS->TR++:GetAll()
TR-->TS--: allTours
loop foreach var tour in allTours
  opt tour.StartTime.Date.Date == SelectedDate.Date
    TS-->SDFTRVM:availability=false
  end
end
  TS-->SDFTRVM--:availability=true

alt availability
  SDFTRVM-->SDFTRW:accept=true
else
  SDFTRVM-->SDFTRW:MessageBox.Show("Error")
end
deactivate SDFTRVM
SDFTRW-->TRAVM--:accept=true
deactivate SDFTRW

opt accept
  TRAVM->ATW++: Display AddTourWindow
end
deactivate TRAVM
deactivate TRAP
ATW->ATVM++:ConfirmTourCommand
ATVM->TR++:MakeID()
TR-->ATVM--:TourId
ATVM->CPR++:AddRange(CheckPointsForListBox)
deactivate CPR
ATVM->TIR++:AddRange(TourImages)
deactivate TIR
ATVM->TR++:Add(Tour)
deactivate TR
ATVM->SRS++:GetById(Id)
SRS->SRR++:GetById(Id)
SRR-->SRS--:simpleRequest
SRS-->ATVM--:simpleRequest
ATVM->SRS++: UpdateStatus(Id, SimpleRequestStatus.APPROVED)
SRS->SRR++: UpdateStatus(Id, SimpleRequestStatus.APPROVED)
deactivate SRR
deactivate SRS
ATVM-> SRTS++:Add(simpleRequestTour)
SRTS->SRTR++: Add(simpleRequestTour)
deactivate SRTR
deactivate SRTS
ATVM-->ATW--: MessageBox.Show("Tour added")
ATW-->U--: MessageBox.Show("Tour added")
@enduml",
  "format": "svg"
}
